---

<MainLayout title="Thomas NÃ¼rk">
	<HeaderLayout>
			<h1 class="sm:text-6xl text-5xl mb-8 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Software Engineer from Germany</h1>
			<p class="text-3xl font-semibold">ðŸ‘‹ Hello!</p>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-xl">My name is Thomas NÃ¼rk, a 21-year-old software developer with a focus on web development based near Dresden, Germany.</p>
			<p class="my-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-xl">Currently, I'm studying computer science at <a class="text-blue-500 hover:underlin" href="https://tu-dresden.de/" target="_blank">TU Dresden</a>. I enjoy seeking out creative solutions to complex problems and building things that are simple but extremely efficient both in performance and data processing.
